data.description: Enjoy this spacious four (4) bedroom, two (3) full bathroom house located in "Stoneybrook North".  This home has an open concept including a gourmet kitchen with quartz counters, a large living room, dining room, stainless steel appliances, master bedroom with a private marble full bath, stone/ceramic hall bath, full bath in lower level, walk-out basement with huge clubroom and bedroom.  This home has recessed lighting throughout, a laundry room, CAC, a driveway, a carport, a storage shed, a very large fenced rear yard and more much.
